      "file_path": "components/slice-analysis-ms/src/main/java/org/onap/slice/analysis/ms/dmaap/MRTopicMonitor.java",
      "patchset_number": 18,
      "line": 20,
      "message": "This may be something be revisited - not sure if long polling feature will be supported part of Strimizi migration (Another question to Fiachra)\n\nBtw DCAE sdk/dmaap-client also support persistence (https://docs.onap.org/projects/onap-dcaegen2/en/latest/sections/sdk/apis.html#configure-custom-persistent-connection)",
